               Death
            </rs>, aged 28.</p>
               <p>Hodges, <rs id="t18010218-47-verdict261" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18010218-47-verdict261" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>, aged 38.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18010218-47-punish262" type="punishmentDescription">
