                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18010218-47-defend288 t18010218-47-punish262"></join>
               Transported for fourteen years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Goddard, <rs id="t18010218-47-verdict263" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18010218-47-verdict263" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               NOT GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Common Serjeant.</p>
